## **ðŸ”¹ Approach / Logic:**

while(iâ‰¥0 jâ‰¥0 carrayâ‰  0)

int bit1 = (iâ‰¥0) ? s1.charAt(i)-â€™0â€™:0 // ternary operator condition ? true : false 

char to int 

